title: #25 Milo Yiannopoulos and Elizabeth Santorum!
description: This week we're joined by two great guests. Milo of #GamerGate fame comes in to educate us on feminists, gay men and transexuals. Then, Elizabeth Santorum shares some personal stories of the campaign trail with her dad! FunDip also goes off on Fat Pride and we talk trannies.
